# bin
some files used to cooperate with the perl script.

## for rnotify
	irssi-connect.sh
	notify-remote.sh
	http://jonathanbeluch.com/blog/2011/03/remote-notify-irssi-screen/

# some basic usage

1. join server and channel
/connect server
/join #channel
2. scroll screen
pageup and pagedown
alt+p   and alt_n	
3. list users
/names
/who

4. talk to user
/query username

5. message prompt
6. change window:
ctrl+P: move to the previous window
ctrl+N: move to the next window
7. auto connect to server:
http://www.irchelp.org/clients/unix/irssi/irssiatboot.html

8. irssi notification
https://github.com/stickster/irssi-libnotify

9. theme:

wget -P ~/.irssi https://raw.githubusercontent.com/msparks/irssiscripts/master/themes/fear2.theme
/set theme fear2

/wc  window close
/set autolog on
/set log
